---

<Layout>
	<div class="title">
		<Word><h1>Meet Our <em>Dedicated</em> Team</h1></Word>
		<Word delay={1}
			><p class="subtitle">
				The Pacific Education Network’s team are core contributors to the cause of free, accessible, and personalized
				tutoring. Without the hard work and dedication from them, our society would not be the same as it is today.
			</p></Word
		>
	</div>
	<div class="spacer" />
	<section class="name-section">
		<h2>Executive Board</h2>
		<p>
			Meet the executives who keep our society thriving! From providing administrative services, scheduling courses,
			marketing, and ensuring student satisfaction, these individuals are the people who have shaped the Pacific Education
			Network’s success.
		</p>
		<div class="board-grid-top">
			{
				boardTop.map(x => (
					<div class="grid-item board-top-item">
						<div class="portrait-image">
							<img src={x.image} />
						</div>
						<h3 class="name">{x.name}</h3>
						<p class="title">{x.title}</p>
					</div>
				))
			}
		</div>
		<div class="board-grid">
			{
				board.map(x => (
					<div class="grid-item board-item">
						<div class="portrait-image">
							<img src={x.image} />
						</div>
						<h3 class="name">{x.name}</h3>
						<p class="title">{x.title}</p>
					</div>
				))
			}
		</div>
	</section>
	<div class="spacer" />
	<section class="name-section">
		<h2>Tutors</h2>
		<p>
			Meet our hardworking tutors who bring Pacific Education Network’s free teaching to life! From publishing resources,
			ensuring consistency, creating opportunities for growth, and fostering genuine connection, these hardworking
			individuals are the reason why the Pacific Education Network is able to empower individuals students in their
			pursuit of knowledge.
		</p>
		<div class="tutor-grid">
			{
				tutors.map(x => (
					<div class="grid-item tutor-item">
						<div class="portrait-image">
							<img src={x.image} />
						</div>
						<h3 class="name">{x.name}</h3>
						<p class="title">{x.title}</p>
					</div>
				))
			}
		</div>
	</section>

	<style>
		.spacer {
			height: 6em;
		}
		.title {
			margin-top: 0.5em;
			font-family: var(--font-montserrat);
			text-align: center;
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			h1 {
				font-size: 2rem;
			}
			.subtitle {
				font-family: var(--font-glacial);
				max-width: 60em;
			}
		}
		.name-section {
			h2 {
				text-align: center;
				font-family: var(--font-montserrat);
				font-size: 1.6em;
				margin-bottom: 0.5em;
			}
			p {
				text-align: center;
			}
			> p {
				max-width: 60em;
				margin: 0 auto;
			}
		}
		.board-grid-top,
		.board-grid,
		.tutor-grid {
			display: grid;
			max-width: 80em;
			margin: 0 auto;
			padding-top: 2em;
			gap: 3em;
			width: fit-content;
		}
		.board-grid-top {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		}
		.board-grid {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
		}
		.tutor-grid {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
		}
		.grid-item {
			text-align: center;
			line-height: 1.1;
			.portrait-image {
				aspect-ratio: 16 / 20;
				background-color: black;
				border: 2px white solid;
				border-radius: 0.8em;
				margin-bottom: 0.5em;
				img {
					width: 100%;
					height: 100%;
				}
			}
			.name {
				margin: 0;
				font-size: 1em;
				font-family: var(--font-montserrat);
			}
			.title {
				margin: 0;
				font-family: var(--font-glacial);
			}
		}
		.board-top-item {
			.portrait-image {
				aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
			}
			width: 13em;
		}
		.board-item {
			width: 10em;
		}
		.tutor-item {
			width: 11em;
		}
	</style>
</Layout>
